Consider all 5 letter "words" made from the letters [`a`] through [`h\text{.}`] (Recall, words are just strings of letters, not necessarily actual English words.)
a.  How many of these words are there total?

    [_______]{32768}

a.  How many of these words contain no repeated letters?

    [_______]{6720}

a.  How many of these words start with the sub-word "aha"?

    [_______]{64}

a.  How many of these words either start with "aha" or end with "bah" or both?

    [_______]{128}

a.  How many of the words containing no repeats also do not contain the sub-word "bad"?

    [_______]{6660}

END_PGML

