BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION
a.  [`8^5 = 32768`] words.
a.  [`8\cdot 7\cdot 6\cdot 5\cdot 4 = 6720`] words.
a.  [`8 \cdot 8 =64`] words.

a.  [`64 + 64 - 0 = 128`] words.
a.  [`(8\cdot 7\cdot 6\cdot 5\cdot 4) - 3\cdot (5\cdot 4) = 6660`] words.   

